    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>什么是《亚洲帮派》？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过占领建筑、召集独特的斗士并发动毁灭性的特殊攻击来征服敌对帮派。游戏提供了共享分屏、在线多人对战和自由混战模式，满足你对好友合作与多人混战的需求，也让游戏体验始终保持新鲜感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/3765f800a296c6a4fb05e0fa36b89cd0.poster.avif?t=1765874328\" width=640 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/3765f800a296c6a4fb05e0fa36b89cd0.webm?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/3765f800a296c6a4fb05e0fa36b89cd0.mp4?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>摘自社区反馈：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“简化的《街头霸王》风格斗……趣味十足，且非常注重技能。”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/670c1fd0ddbb90f0325a01c1f74c31bc.poster.avif?t=1765874328\" width=640 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/670c1fd0ddbb90f0325a01c1f74c31bc.webm?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/670c1fd0ddbb90f0325a01c1f74c31bc.mp4?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关键特性</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四位独特的帮派首领</strong><br>掌控每位英雄背后独特的微机制和个性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>六种战力强悍的单位类型</strong><br>部署暴徒、功夫大师、相扑手、忍者等单位，提升战术深度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏即时战略</strong><br>夺取敌人的地盘，巩固你的阵地，并派出斗士们展开无情攻击。在高风险的单挑中击败他们的头目，夺取最终胜利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级&amp;专业化</strong><br>为你自己和帮派定制并升级占领的建筑。从防御姿态、猛烈打击等12种特殊攻击中挑选4种，打造你的完美阵容，并释放它们来扭转战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样的多人模式</strong><br>在多种四人模式中组队或对战。在占山为王、群殴和全面征服模式中战斗，所有模式均可在线或本地分屏进行对抗或合作游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>群殴模式生存</strong><br>与最多三位好友一起，抵御一波又一波的攻击，防守你的地盘。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义地图编辑器（制作中）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造你自己的地图并挑战社区！游戏完全支持Steam创意工坊，你可以分享自己的创作，并从其他玩家那里下载无数新战场。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/1e100272f3ff5029ef5d47b118ec4287.poster.avif?t=1765874328\" width=640 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/1e100272f3ff5029ef5d47b118ec4287.webm?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/1e100272f3ff5029ef5d47b118ec4287.mp4?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>下一步计划</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抢先体验版游戏仍在积极更新中，包括更智能的 AI、更多地图和游戏修正。加入我们的 Discord，共同塑造未来、测试新模式，并一起创建全新地图！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/4e5074ac7a1a689e3aeecaaa7f5feccb.poster.avif?t=1765874328\" width=640 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/4e5074ac7a1a689e3aeecaaa7f5feccb.webm?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382670/extras/4e5074ac7a1a689e3aeecaaa7f5feccb.mp4?t=1765874328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
